          captivate audiences and drive business growth. We combine aesthetic
          excellence with strategic thinking to create digital experiences that
          users love and remember.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
