      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-6"
          >
            Design Excellence That Drives Business Results
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-4">
            <p>
              Great web design is more than just beautiful visuals—it's the
              perfect marriage of aesthetics, functionality, and strategic
              thinking. At Codebrand, we create web designs that don't just look
              stunning, they drive measurable business results by guiding users
              through intuitive, engaging experiences that convert visitors into
              loyal customers. Every design decision we make is rooted in user
              research, brand strategy, and conversion optimization principles.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our design philosophy centers on understanding your users deeply
              and crafting experiences that resonate with their needs,
              preferences, and behaviors. We combine cutting-edge design trends
              with timeless principles of visual hierarchy, color psychology,
              typography, and user interface design to create websites that
              stand out in crowded markets. Whether you need a complete website
              redesign, landing page optimization, or a comprehensive design
              system, we have the expertise to elevate your digital presence.
            </p>
            <p>
              We believe exceptional web design should be accessible,
              responsive, and performant across all devices and screen sizes.
              Mobile-first design isn't just a buzzword for us—it's a
              fundamental approach that ensures your website delivers
              pixel-perfect experiences whether users access it from
              smartphones, tablets, or desktop computers. With over 60% of web
              traffic coming from mobile devices, responsive design is no longer
              optional—it's essential for business success.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our collaborative design process keeps you involved every step of
              the way. From initial concepts and wireframes to high-fidelity
              mockups and interactive prototypes, you'll see your vision come to
              life through regular reviews and iterations. We use
              industry-standard design tools and methodologies to ensure
              seamless handoff to development teams, maintaining design
              integrity from concept to final implementation. The result is a
              cohesive, polished digital product that exceeds your expectations
              and delights your users.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
